WEBVTT

00:00:06.795 --> 00:00:08.055
Udadisi:

00:00:08.055 --> 00:00:09.863
Baraka au laana?

00:00:09.863 --> 00:00:11.603
Utata wa hili fumbo

00:00:11.603 --> 00:00:13.553
iliwekewa kwa Wagiriki

00:00:13.553 --> 00:00:15.913
kwa umbo la dhana la Pandora.

00:00:15.913 --> 00:00:17.033
Wahenga wanasema,

00:00:17.033 --> 00:00:18.743
alikuwa mwanamke wa kwanza mfaji,

00:00:18.743 --> 00:00:23.413
udadisi wake ulipeleka ugunduzi wa
mambo mengi kusogea.

00:00:23.413 --> 00:00:27.076
Pandora alipewa pumzi na
Hephaestus, mungu wa moto,

00:00:27.076 --> 00:00:31.266
ambae aliomba msaada wa wenzie
ili amfanye kuwa maridadi